Release Notes:
===============

Google Search Appliance Connector for IBM FileNet P8 3.5

This document contains the release notes for Google Search Appliance Connector for IBM FileNet P8 3.5
The following sections describe the release in detail and provide information that supplements the main documentation.
See the Issues Tab on the Code Site for the current list of known issues and workarounds.

Web Site: http://code.google.com/p/google-enterprise-connector-file/issues/list


Release 2.6.0, June 02, 2010
==========================

Introduction
------------------
This is the patch release of this product. See the product website for a complete description.

Version Compatibility
-----------------------
Upgrading earlier versions, lower than 2.0.x, with this version will not work.
This version works with Connector Manager version 2.6.x.

Platform Support
------------------
The connector can be installed on x86/x64 Windows (2003/2008) and Linux environments.

